Recommends: linux-headers-generic | linux-headers-amd64 | linux-headers
Description: DKMS driver for Tenda AIC8800DC and AIC8800D80 adapters
 Tenda 1.0.13 Wi-Fi driver with W311MI-specific configuration and USB IDs
 2604:0013, 2604:0014, 2604:001f, and 2604:0020. The package includes DC
 and D80 firmware, a USB mass-storage mode-switch rule, module auto-loading,
 and DKMS integration for kernel upgrades.
